{"tid":851853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大今次絕食完全多鳩如！泛民式階段性退卻笑死人 369","createTime":"2018-10-07T12:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T14:02:11.000Z","uid":49388,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4062c473337d520e875aab4bfaa8e82a27915baf","tid":851853,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"呢單「抗爭」真係好有趣，首先理大學生會將一半民主牆變成「連儂牆」，廢除咗大部份守則，其後校方要求學生會「還原」民主牆，否則校方就會管理改變咗用途嗰一半民主牆，之後有學生絕食，然後有飯民議員到場聲稱學生及出聯署，到頭先學生會終於肯「還原民主牆」，停止絕食。咁有幾樣嘢本隊長真係諗唔明。<br />\n<br />\n第一，民主牆本身已經可以讓學生自由發表意見，學生會將一半民主牆改成連儂牆，限死咗個主題，其實咁做先係「收窄」咗言論自由，校方要求「還原」真係唔合理咩？<br />\n<br />\n第二，學生會明明知道「還原」民主牆就可以有返民主牆全部嘅管理權，咁點解仲要絕食呢？到今日學生會同意「還原」民主牆以及停止絕食，其實搞咁大場大龍鳳究竟係想爭取啲咩呢？中間絕食嗰下「升級」，係咪多餘呢？<br />\n<br />\n有無人理解到，可以解釋我聽呀？.？☹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/203010_7ad75e560b35c7ea9d993ddcd8a34c50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F203010_7ad75e560b35c7ea9d993ddcd8a34c50.png&h=317af89d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉貼至狙擊政棍小隊 fb <br />\n<br />\n理大學生會會長王𩓙恆主張返回學聯建立大台<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/203243_7cb5285de6141fdbd8c98975907d7a72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F203243_7cb5285de6141fdbd8c98975907d7a72.png&h=9e6e09af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多名親建制團體「珍惜群組」成員約下午四時到理大校園「踩場」示威，並大肆批評學生，其後向校方代表遞交請願信後離開。另外，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">23名泛民立法會議員聯署致函理大校長唐偉章，要求對方盡快與絕食學生會面，以理性方法解決問題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一日內已經有23條泛民聯署，你話條莊唔係泛民背景真係無人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前本土莊出事幾可泛民咁快有聯署？唔好話聯署，反應都未必有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ecb4a149c627064051d139498544cd80a216bd","tid":851853,"uid":73200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5d71e17c0832cdce50de87abf246f5c35f37d46","tid":851853,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"有冇人話我知絕食既原因係邊到？"},{"pid":"8377b9955991d4dcbe7e30dfa7eb79edd9cdf6aa","tid":851853,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"人呢？"},{"pid":"40ef9e6916fd7f8c50b8bffd61488710d0961b9c","tid":851853,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"理大孔子學院既課程是否還可以當理大本科生學分？"},{"pid":"d838b85d41a0de26d7bcbff1a3b15aaa6c6b4f1a","tid":851853,"uid":2436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f867fb98655e46722d289a38f4aca77f757ee844","tid":851853,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ccd268813b3b6ef7979aa804d6a9f8d69d6ed05","tid":851853,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"神駒又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa594d0d862cceb023990ae80c8d5e0e6bfb952","tid":851853,"uid":38395,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:49:36.000Z","msg":"算啦 呢到咁多人黃屍 你覺得佢地會答你咩樓主"},{"pid":"50965686c9e64c7ad805126f3ea060f4dbfb6270","tid":851853,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"理大學生會個聲明有無提連農牆依家係咩狀況? 存在定取消左?"},{"pid":"5b97acc7870187f52817428c2bb921401232e988","tid":851853,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"關囝呢"}]}